Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.20,0:00:48.20,jinggao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}翻译：Rcat；校对：白い流星；后期：zipwinmax；繁体化：黑羽侖人。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:45.44,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}　　　　　　"自那以后"和"从今往后"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.18,0:00:22.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.70,0:00:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  已经是春天了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.51,0:00:51.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.79,0:00:54.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.00,0:00:56.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  等很久了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.17,0:00:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.63,0:01:00.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上出发？还是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.39,0:01:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先去吃点东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.17,0:01:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.55,0:01:17.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我好久没进城  有点紧张  所以没怎么吃早饭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.93,0:01:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠  掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.43,0:01:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  要你来陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.52,0:01:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  本身我也想在大屏幕上看看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.75,0:01:31.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就当是放松吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.72,0:01:33.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明年就要高考了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.98,0:01:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.27,0:01:38.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.55,0:01:39.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.14,0:01:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开学后你就是部团的前辈了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.88,0:01:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈…吗  我？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.35,0:01:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.26,0:01:49.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.72,0:01:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好好练习吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.79,0:01:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.69,0:01:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这个我也很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.39,0:01:57.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你自秋天以后就没有比过了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.41,0:02:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  部团那边很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:04.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我不会输了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.05,0:02:12.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.85,0:02:13.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.78,0:02:14.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的笑容！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.01,0:02:23.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}（超剑站队  集结！四圣兽的战士们）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.11,0:02:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超剑战队  Blade Braver
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.24,0:02:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.49,0:02:37.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个气势！十字！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.62,0:02:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.56,0:02:43.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  超越你自己吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要赢  不要再…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.26,0:02:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈德是不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.25,0:02:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈格尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.66,0:03:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道复活了？！Silver Blade
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家上！最终变形
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:08.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨大布雷巴机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.26,0:03:13.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大圣剑·布雷球三位一体冲击！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.24,0:03:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.83,0:03:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:39.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷巴也蛮帅的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.96,0:03:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  施奈德也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.15,0:03:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年级啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.38,0:04:07.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道今年能有多少新生加入呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:10.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:15.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  有没有荧光灯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:20.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在那边  小忍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:24.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿诚  你不觉得这太不讲道理了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.15,0:04:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.17,0:04:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我们非要参加剑道部啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.48,0:04:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得我们通过考试
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:33.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正要开始缤纷的高中生活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这起点为什么要是什么面啊手啊的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣嘛  而且运动也可以锻炼身体啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.37,0:04:43.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样是锻炼身体  我宁愿选择其他运动！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.08,0:04:47.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乒乓球啦  袋球啦  卡巴迪啦  翔蹴啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.78,0:04:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的这些好像都没有部团啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.11,0:04:50.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乒乓球也没有？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:55.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之去看看道场吧  反正人都来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.63,0:04:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  归根结底
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.97,0:05:02.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最讨厌剑道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.54,0:05:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:10.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看根本没人嘛  回去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:12.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么着急嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.44,0:05:15.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.31,0:05:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:19.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是新生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.24,0:05:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新生？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.12,0:05:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让我们参观一下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.91,0:05:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  请进请进
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.85,0:05:31.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新生…这怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:35.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  有什么能让我们参观的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:43.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人还没有来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没来  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:49.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  待下去也是浪费时间  回去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:54.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请再等等吧  大家马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.23,0:05:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谁能快点来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.86,0:06:00.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:05.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.45,0:06:07.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二年级的东
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.31,0:06:12.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  其他人都还没有来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.67,0:06:16.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们做点什么给他们参观一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.59,0:06:19.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们好像很无聊的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.91,0:06:23.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  可不能让他们觉得无聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  请不用在意我们  就像平日一样就好  前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.56,0:06:31.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前…辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚他叫我们前辈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.35,0:06:40.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们两个是我们入部以来的第一批后辈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.52,0:06:41.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:46.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说我们的实力和新生员挂着钩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.49,0:06:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了  总之在部长前辈老师回来之前留住他们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.82,0:06:56.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠我们的「技艺」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:57.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「技艺」？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.94,0:07:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在表演空手夺白刃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:08.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里是白刃了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.33,0:07:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.64,0:07:12.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失手了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是普通地比上一场…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:18.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.76,0:07:20.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫崎同学  请你表演一个什么吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:22.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然搞什么东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:25.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说他们是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:29.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.82,0:07:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.55,0:07:46.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:49.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和剑道八竿子打不着嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:55.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了好了  小忍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:55.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了算了  宫崎同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个一年级搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.42,0:07:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还特地表演给她看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.51,0:08:03.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得还是普通地比上一场给他们看…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.99,0:08:05.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热闹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:07.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.39,0:08:12.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听人家说哦  那个一年级的好嚣张哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.24,0:08:14.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年级？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:16.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想入部？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.21,0:08:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.11,0:08:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是来参观的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.82,0:08:19.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有练过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.23,0:08:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  但是我有护具
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:25.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是哥哥他们让给我们的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:29.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说自己不练扔着太可惜  妈妈就硬塞给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.96,0:08:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  的确有这种事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.19,0:08:36.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过既然来了  就留下来看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:39.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要加入以后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.17,0:08:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说您是部长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.78,0:08:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  为什么这么看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.55,0:08:46.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为您看起来最正经
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长是段君他哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.54,0:08:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是部长哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:54.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本是个栗子么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:56.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说谁是栗子？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.91,0:08:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫崎同学  道场内禁止暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.04,0:09:02.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个一年级的真叫人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.45,0:09:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:05.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小忍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要紧吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  脚跪酸了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.33,0:09:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁让你小看剑道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:15.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…这大概没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.00,0:09:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才讨厌剑道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,护具又难看  又土气  还臭得要命！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:24.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小忍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.11,0:09:27.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在练剑道  有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.24,0:09:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑道很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得没错～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.40,0:09:41.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.79,0:09:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在啊  诸位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:47.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是春假过后就引退吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.93,0:09:50.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别随便就赶我们走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.26,0:09:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还会参加县大赛的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.45,0:09:54.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全都听见了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.58,0:09:56.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年级诸位！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.96,0:09:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在对剑道还有这样的偏见已经过时了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:00.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时值当下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No No No No
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.86,0:10:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因时值当下才要Let's剑道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.53,0:10:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on together
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑道的护具的确又笨重又土气还有味道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.99,0:10:13.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但练过的话绝对很有意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.00,0:10:16.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.12,0:10:17.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.46,0:10:19.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:24.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.87,0:10:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气势上来咯！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.87,0:11:02.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.57,0:11:05.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都好像变了一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.34,0:11:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  很帅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:11.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.59,0:11:15.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  大家都好像乐在其中的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.19,0:11:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这就是室江高中剑道部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.69,0:11:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很像一年前的我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.60,0:11:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.24,0:11:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！停～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.94,0:11:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  这就是剑道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厉害的魄力  我很吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.75,0:11:48.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是她  虽然不大但很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠啊  因为是全国水平的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.46,0:11:53.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点兴趣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.87,0:11:58.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我们是不折不扣的初学者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能变得像前辈你们一样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:03.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就要看练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.23,0:12:07.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过就算是初学者也没什么好担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:08.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要知道我们的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:12.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  会议延长了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.47,0:12:14.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师你好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.99,0:12:17.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我去换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:19.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顾问可是一号初学者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  这半年来我作为顾问来给大家指导…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:31.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不对  是来被大家指导
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.44,0:12:33.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真老实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.45,0:12:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要暂时和大家分开一段时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.10,0:12:37.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.96,0:12:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.39,0:12:41.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:42.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:46.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我有孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.56,0:12:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦——！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.68,0:12:50.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要暂时休产假
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:52.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩女孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.11,0:12:54.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没查过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几个月大了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.62,0:12:59.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个月左右
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.49,0:13:00.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您丈夫知道了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.29,0:13:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜您
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.41,0:13:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜您
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:17.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.17,0:13:27.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才三个月嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.99,0:13:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下个换我  下个换我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:34.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛和指导虽然可以继续拜托小珠爸爸和内村先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.42,0:13:37.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但顾问该怎么解决？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:42.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再去找别人吧  比如教导主任
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.95,0:13:44.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这个不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:47.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经拜托好人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:49.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是会剑道的老师吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.63,0:13:51.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  很厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:53.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.34,0:13:57.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石桥老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.70,0:14:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的～这样怎么行嘛  我都说别再来部团了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这可不是你一个人的身体了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.31,0:14:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才三个月嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.71,0:14:13.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的顾问是石桥老师吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.88,0:14:16.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  不是老师的老公嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.76,0:14:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是石桥老师你不是兼职两所学校的顾问么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.72,0:14:24.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不就没法做其他学校的顾问老师了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.48,0:14:28.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么着急  我才不是顾问  我也没那时间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:32.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的顾问是这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:33.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我我我…我的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:42.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…布雷巴！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.47,0:14:45.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姓布雷巴  名布雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.14,0:14:48.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人称布雷巴布雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.26,0:14:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多指教！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:55.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:57.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}那搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.49,0:14:58.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:15:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…初次见面  剑道部的各位 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.70,0:15:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.45,0:15:07.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师！老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…搞什么啊  纪梨乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:06.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细看清楚  我现在可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.45,0:15:11.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都叫你正常点出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.94,0:15:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来  老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:33.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为代理休产假的吉河老师  我复职了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.31,0:15:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  那个理事长的夫人的大妈朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.42,0:15:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她没说什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.36,0:15:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大妈搬家了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.42,0:15:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是邻居  所以也没什么影响力了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:50.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  就是多亏了吉河老师和林老师的推荐书
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.66,0:15:51.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不会剑道  但行动力还是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:58.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样  今后多指教了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.92,0:15:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.89,0:16:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:05.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  今天我们来参观
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.67,0:16:09.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛是嘛  我们部非常欢迎有兴趣的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:15.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太着急了老师  你还不是正式的顾问吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.88,0:16:17.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么见外啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:21.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫石田虎侍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:22.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:24.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩佐 诚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:26.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外山 忍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.94,0:16:28.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩佐？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:30.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外山…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:33.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的哥哥过去是剑道部的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.70,0:16:36.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…不过好像不怎么出席的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:38.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们认识他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩佐的弟弟和外山的妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点不像
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.24,0:16:47.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  特别是岩佐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小诚  小忍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.68,0:16:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.99,0:16:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不强迫你们  但如果有兴趣的话请你们一定要加入
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.76,0:17:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.03,0:17:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连你们哥哥的份一起来练剑道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:07.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会考虑的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.55,0:17:10.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是个好日子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.89,0:17:13.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是室江高剑道部的全新起点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.04,0:17:17.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  戴护具
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.80,0:17:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么长时间  我要看看你们有什么长进
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.67,0:17:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.78,0:17:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的护具呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:27.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带了一副来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.35,0:17:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他这是等不及想和大家比试呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.46,0:17:36.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙一点没成长呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.08,0:17:56.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！今天就练到精疲力尽为止吧！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:17:57.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:17:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的部团
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.21,0:18:04.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈后辈老师学生搅成一团  大家好像朋友一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:07.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！来吧！小珠！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.42,0:18:08.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.78,0:18:09.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.61,0:18:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面有效
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:17.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复职庆祝的话  你就再搞得热闹点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你庆祝就心存感激吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.34,0:18:22.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往后我可就没这闲钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.50,0:18:24.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是够快的啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉河老师打电话来的时候  真是吓我一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:31.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自那以后都怎么过的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.37,0:18:40.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经阿伸的介绍  上船工作去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.69,0:18:41.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有帮帮家里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:45.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下就光在练空挥了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.36,0:18:47.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空挥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:54.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  工作过后挥上几小时上百次直到精疲力尽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:58.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才能没什么烦恼走过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:02.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才能继续保持一定的水平吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.78,0:19:04.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你一定退步了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.43,0:19:08.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为到了这个年纪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.01,0:19:10.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才终于发现
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.31,0:19:15.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来空挥是那么累那么让人着迷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.85,0:19:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才刚刚开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.20,0:19:25.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是累  还是入迷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.27,0:19:28.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.95,0:19:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人  空挥是指棒球？还是高尔夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.32,0:19:37.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是剑道——！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.33,0:19:43.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.93,0:19:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.88,0:19:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在练摆振吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.16,0:19:52.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因为换了新竹剑  所以想早点熟悉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:55.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就自然而然的练起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.33,0:19:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你遇上什么好事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.10,0:19:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.99,0:20:04.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没和你比一场了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是长大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.73,0:20:25.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面——！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:27.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面——！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:18.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.12,0:21:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在  是高中二年级学生了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.27,0:21:37.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢剑道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.20,0:21:57.31,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}透きとおる陽射しが好き
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.85,0:22:03.33,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}みんなの背中輝いているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.17,0:22:09.31,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}同じ日々目指してるから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.90,0:22:14.88,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}もう寂しくならないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.83,0:22:19.58,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}誰もひとりぼっちじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.85,0:22:22.57,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}心まで立ち止まる時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.75,0:22:25.55,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}その笑顔でみんなが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.73,0:22:28.92,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}見守ってくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.81,0:22:33.48,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}だから眩しさに飛びこんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.69,0:22:36.52,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}青空に届く{\fs26}POWER
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.73,0:22:38.84,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ひるまずにひたすらに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.03,0:22:41.66,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この道を行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.84,0:22:45.42,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}いつかときめきの頂点に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.69,0:22:48.38,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}生まれるよ虹の{\fs26}STORY
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.63,0:22:51.04,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}苦しくて焦っても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.35,0:22:53.90,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}乗り越えられるきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.17,0:22:55.89,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私たちの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.22,0:23:00.80,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(0,300)}{\fs26}BAMBOOBEAT{\r}を鳴らして
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.20,0:21:57.31,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}喜欢着纯净的阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.85,0:22:03.33,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}我们的背后都闪耀着光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.17,0:22:09.31,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}每一日都朝着同一个目标
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.90,0:22:14.88,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}就再也不会感到寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.83,0:22:19.58,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}谁也不会是孤单一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.85,0:22:22.57,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}若是心中彷徨无法前进的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.75,0:22:25.55,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}我会用这份笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.73,0:22:28.92,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}把大家守护
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.81,0:22:33.48,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}因此光彩夺目地展翅高飞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.69,0:22:36.52,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}那份力量直达蓝天之上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.73,0:22:38.84,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}毫不畏惧  毫不分心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.03,0:22:41.66,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}向着前程全力进发
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.84,0:22:45.42,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}直到心跳的顶点时分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.69,0:22:48.38,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}就会绽放出彩虹的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.63,0:22:51.04,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}就算再多艰辛苦难
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.35,0:22:53.90,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}我也一定能越过去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.17,0:22:55.89,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}让我们共有的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.22,0:23:00.80,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}{\fad(0,300)}竹剑节奏响彻永远
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.51,0:23:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  再见
